    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Linings of chimneys constructed of special heat-resistant materials to prevent fire, smoke, and gases from spreading to surrounding spaces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
